    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏介绍</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Binarycurse》是一款充满困难的悬疑益智冒险游戏。玩家扮演一个主角，意外发现了一台神秘的旧电脑，开始了一段揭露令人震惊的真相的旅程。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316170/extras/ce90c315a065f1ea54d18c8754656c07.avif?t=1732241326\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316170/extras_big/ce90c315a065f1ea54d18c8754656c07.avif?t=1732241326 width=800 height=444 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏玩法：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >首先完成第一个挑战，通过锁屏界面提示，解开锁屏密码</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入界面后，通过鼠标点击进行操作</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >查找隐藏信息或密码</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁锁定的文件夹</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过解密文件推动情节发展</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316170/extras/111b877ecc4b01f606f01b4d6c19b48f.avif?t=1732241326\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316170/extras_big/111b877ecc4b01f606f01b4d6c19b48f.avif?t=1732241326 width=800 height=442 /></span></p></li></ul>",
